Lenovo to Sell 1 Million Tablets in China, Shanghai Daily Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-03-29T18:40:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/lenovo-to-sell-1-million-tablets-in-china-shanghai-daily-says.html
Lenovo Group Ltd. (992)  aims to sell 1
million of its LePad tablet computers in the Chinese market this
year through major electronics retailers, Shanghai Daily said,
citing General Manager Chen Xudong.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  